  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/d89b129c6f16d86cdf63dfc33d9e5943.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/d89b129c6f16d86cdf63dfc33d9e5943.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span>The genial inventor is back with new logical enigmas written in a book!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the answers, unlock the Cryptex, and see what awaits you in the next level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/15336948a5701ecfed1da936467d262e.avif?t=1751521500\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/79a53cf9b26bb89317c84210d4f2d1a8.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/79a53cf9b26bb89317c84210d4f2d1a8.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span><strong>The Da Vinci Cryptex 2</strong> is a brainteasing game with 50 unique riddles. The more you solve them, the harder the puzzles become</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning</strong>: this IQ game may be addictive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/3e836304ee6269e759860f2a1869de7a.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/3e836304ee6269e759860f2a1869de7a.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 50 unique handcrafted puzzles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Hints available (click the bulb button to get a hint)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Astonishing graphics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Captivating background music</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're a fan of puzzles, word games, brain thinking, mind games, IQ logic riddles, and enigmas, <strong>The Da Vinci Cryptex</strong> is the game for you, have fun in your spare time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/d89b129c6f16d86cdf63dfc33d9e5943.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/d89b129c6f16d86cdf63dfc33d9e5943.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span>The genial inventor is back with new logical enigmas written in a book!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the answers, unlock the Cryptex, and see what awaits you in the next level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/15336948a5701ecfed1da936467d262e.avif?t=1751521500\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/79a53cf9b26bb89317c84210d4f2d1a8.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/79a53cf9b26bb89317c84210d4f2d1a8.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span><strong>The Da Vinci Cryptex 2</strong> is a brainteasing game with 50 unique riddles. The more you solve them, the harder the puzzles become</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning</strong>: this IQ game may be addictive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/3e836304ee6269e759860f2a1869de7a.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/3e836304ee6269e759860f2a1869de7a.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 50 unique handcrafted puzzles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Hints available (click the bulb button to get a hint)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Astonishing graphics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Captivating background music</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're a fan of puzzles, word games, brain thinking, mind games, IQ logic riddles, and enigmas, <strong>The Da Vinci Cryptex</strong> is the game for you, have fun in your spare time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717780/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521500 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
